message.1
	There's a strange sound
message.2
	The book is in bad condtion but I can make out the title:\n`Treasure Island`. There's a word written in blood in the\nflyleaf: `YOHO` and a message:\n\n`Long John Silver left 2 treasures on Treasure Island`
message.3
	Nothing happens
message.4
	There's something there all right. Maybe I should
message.5
	That's not very smart
message.6
	I may need to say a MAGIC word here!
message.7
	Everything spins around and suddenly I'm elsewhere...
message.8
	Torch is lit
message.9
	I was wrong, I guess its not a mongoose cause the snakes bit it!
message.10
	I'm snake bit
message.11
	Parrot attacks snakes and drives them off
message.12
	Pirate won't let me
message.13
	Its locked
message.14
	Its open
message.15
	There are a set of plans in it
message.16
	Not while I'm carrying it
message.17
	Crocs stop me
message.18
	Sorry I can't
message.19
	Wrong game you silly goose!
message.20
	I don't have it
message.21
	Pirate grabs rum and scuttles off chortling
message.22
	...I think its me, Hee Hee.
message.23
	Its nailed to the floor!
message.24
	Yoho ho and a ...
