	I slipped and fell...
message.30
	Something falls out
message.31
	They're plans to build the Jolly Roger (a Pirate ship!)\nYou'll need: hammer, nails, lumber, anchor, sails, and a keel.
message.32
	I've no container
message.33
	It soaks into the ground
message.34
	Too dry, fish vanish.
message.35
	Pirate awakens and says `Aye matey we be casting off soon`\nHe then VANISHES!
message.36
	What a waste...
message.37
	I've no crew
message.38
	Pirate says: `Aye matey we be needing a map first`.
message.39
	After a day at sea we set anchor off of a sandy beach.\nAll Ashore who's going Ashore...
message.40
	Try: `WEIGH ANCHOR`
message.41
	There's a map in it
message.42
	Its a map to Treasure Island. At the bottom it says:\n`30 paces then dig!`
message.43
	* Welcome to Adventure number 2: `pirate adventure`\nby Alexis & Scott Adams, dedicated: Ted Heeren & Paul Sharland\nRemember you can always ask for `help`.\n
